⸻

🧠 Core Concept

Your SDK does 3 things:

1. 🔍 System Detection (AUTO-TUNE)

Detects:
	•	CPU (cores, cache, AVX support)
	•	GPU (NVIDIA / AMD / Intel)
	•	VRAM + RAM
	•	Disk speed

# core/system_probe.py
import subprocess

def detect_gpu():
    out = subprocess.getoutput("lspci | grep -i vga")
    if "NVIDIA" in out:
        return "nvidia"
    elif "AMD" in out:
        return "amd"
    return "intel"

def detect_cpu():
    return subprocess.getoutput("lscpu")

def detect_ram():
    return subprocess.getoutput("free -h")


⸻

2. 🤖 AI Inference Engine (Adaptive Backend)

Switch automatically:
	•	NVIDIA → TensorRT
	•	AMD → ONNX / ROCm
	•	CPU → OpenVINO fallback

# ai/inference_engine.py
class AIEngine:
    def __init__(self, backend):
        self.backend = backend

    def load_model(self, path):
        if self.backend == "nvidia":
            print("Using TensorRT")
        elif self.backend == "amd":
            print("Using ONNX Runtime")
        else:
            print("Using CPU fallback")

    def infer(self, frame):
        return frame  # placeholder


